N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 470.8 - Fees

State Regulations

There is no fee for the processing of an application for a
license, except in cases where new fingerprints are required and a fee is
imposed by the Division of Criminal Justice Services for processing of the
fingerprints. Notes
